Using "RC_Core.rcm"
; Spawn-init for the Wounded Scout flavour NPCs in the wilds (Test Zone).
; Runs once at spawn (the spawn's `script` slot, like Spawn_Test.rsl). Names the
; NPC so it reads as an intentional survivor rather than a nameless test dummy.
;
; SetName is privileged -> this script is on Privileged Scripts.dat.

Function Main()

	NPC = Actor()
	SetName(NPC, "Wounded Scout")

	Return

End Function
